                                        "_animation": "fadeInUp",
                                        "animation_duration": "slow"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "43fcf753",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>At BalancePoint, our skilled physiotherapists are dedicated to helping clients overcome physical limitations, reduce pain, and regain their optimal level of function and mobility. Through a comprehensive, holistic approach, we empower individuals to take an active role in their recovery and improve function, and regain their independence wellness journey.</p><p>Chronic or persistent pain can significantly impact an individual's quality of life. Our physiotherapists utilize evidence-based modalities, such as therapeutic exercises, electrical stimulation, and specialized manual techniques.</p>",
                                        "paragraph_spacing": {
                                            "unit": "px",
                                            "size": 24,
                                            "sizes": []
                                        },
